{"seat":"W2-A","slice":"152 R1 inert-gate + R2 dead-paths","findings":[{"id":"W2-A-1","severity":"P1","packet":"152","file":".opencode/hooks/pre-commit","line":"40","title":"Agent mirror-sync gate is inert — points at deleted checker path, silently warns-and-skips","evidence":"L40 MIRROR_CHECKER=\"$REPO_ROOT/.opencode/skills/deep-improvement/scripts/check-agent-mirror-sync.cjs\" — `ls` confirms MISSING; real file now at .opencode/skills/deep-loop-workflows/deep-improvement/scripts/check-agent-mirror-sync.cjs. L48-49 `[[ ! -f \"$MIRROR_CHECKER\" ]]` → echoes WARNING and falls through (no exit) to exit 0.","why":"When staged agent files are committed the local gate no longer runs check-agent-mirror-sync.cjs, so a desynced .opencode/.claude/.codex mirror can be committed with only a stderr warning — a protective gate is dead, not failing closed.","fix":"Update L40 to MIRROR_CHECKER=\"$REPO_ROOT/.opencode/skills/deep-loop-workflows/deep-improvement/scripts/check-agent-mirror-sync.cjs\"."},{"id":"W2-A-2","severity":"P2","packet":"152","file":".opencode/skills/sk-code/references/smart_routing.md","line":"300","title":"Dead drift-guard path + broken runnable npx command (deleted deep-improvement/scripts)","evidence":"L300 names drift guard `.opencode/skills/deep-improvement/scripts/skill-benchmark/tests/sk-code-router-sync.vitest.ts` and tells reader to run `npx vitest run skill-benchmark/tests/sk-code-router-sync.vitest.ts` from `.opencode/skills/deep-improvement/scripts` — that cwd no longer exists, so the cd/npx fails.","why":"Doc points to a non-existent test path and a repro command whose working dir is gone; the named drift guard can't be located or run from the cited location.","fix":"Repoint to .opencode/skills/deep-loop-workflows/deep-improvement/scripts/skill-benchmark/tests/sk-code-router-sync.vitest.ts and update the `from` cwd to .opencode/skills/deep-loop-workflows/deep-improvement/scripts."},{"id":"W2-A-3","severity":"P2","packet":"152","file":".opencode/ski